{"tid":2456922,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"721白衣人｜法官裁定案件表面證供成立 預料「飛天南」明早出庭自辯","createTime":"2021-03-22T09:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T07:49:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f4720624d3ada5e67934bc29db5f53ee356ff9ff","tid":2456922,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T09:14:19.000Z","msg":"元朗7.21白衣人暴動及傷人案續審，聆訊踏入第20天，區域法院法官葉佐文聽罷控方案情以及雙方中段陳詞後，裁定案件表面證供成立，各被告須就控罪答辯。第六被告「飛天南」吳偉南預料明早將會自辯，他另有3名辯方證人，其餘被告傾向不出庭作供。<br />\n<br />\n六名受審被告依序為運輸公司東主王志榮（55歲）、工程公司東主黃英傑（48歲）、西鐵燒烤樂園東主鄧懷琛（60歲）、「飛天南」吳偉南（57歲）、八鄉鄉事委員會居民代表兼橫台山河瀝背村村長鄧英斌（61歲），以及維修技工蔡立基（40歲）。另有兩名被告被告「懵良」林觀良（48歲）及「肥林」林啟明（43歲）承認暴動罪，還柙候判。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210322/MXVLCB6DHBCK5O4QSG3SH7BPPU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210322%2FMXVLCB6DHBCK5O4QSG3SH7BPPU%2F&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbfkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=67a7b2d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210322%2FMXVLCB6DHBCK5O4QSG3SH7BPPU%2F&h=d479e286\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210322/MXVLCB6DHBCK5O4QSG3SH7BPPU/</a>"},{"pid":"0401db57384469a309eae568503f2da43502b2ad","tid":2456922,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T09:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71c80b55707b439b346653e214fa4c44eb2a4d8","tid":2456922,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T09:15:37.000Z","msg":"我直入元朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0b9dae8635a7